name: Groupergram
body:
#Groupergram

An application that displays the Instagram Images with #groupergram. This project uses [FlatUIKit](https://github.com/Grouper/FlatUIKit), [GMGridView](https://github.com/gmoledina/GMGridView), [SDURLCache](https://github.com/rs/SDURLCache), [SDWebImage](https://github.com/rs/SDWebImage), [UAModalPanel](https://github.com/coneybeare/UAModalPanel), and [AFNetworking](https://github.com/AFNetworking/AFNetworking). Artwork was taken from the [Grouper](https://www.joingrouper.com/) website.
